comment: [Incidental or immaterial] McCollum (POR) grabs Patterson's (TOR) jersey on the perimeter.
Patterson (TOR) maintains legal guarding position on the drive to the basket by McCollum (POR) and absorbs the contact.
McCollum (POR) gathers the ball and then takes three steps.
Plumlee (POR) makes incidental contact with Lowry (TOR) that does not affect his SQBR.
[Observable in enhanced video] RATR shows that Lowry (TOR) moves his pivot foot.
Aminu (POR) makes marginal contact with Nogueira (TOR) that does not dislodge him from his legal guarding position.
Harkless (POR) legally contests DeRozan's (TOR) jump shot attempt and makes incidental contact that does not affect his ability to land.
Aminu (POR) commits a take foul on Joseph (TOR).
Lowry (TOR) makes foot to foot contact with McCollum (POR) that affects his driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on DeRozan (TOR).
Harkless (NOP) makes incidental contact with DeRozan (TOR) during rebounding.
